 the plasma not only at the entrance but\nalso the exit side of the ps-pulse enhances the proton beam collimation,\nincreases significantly the number of high energy protons, as well as their\nmaximum energy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Sep 2020 16:13:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-24"}
