-predicted image positions is only\n0.40\", which is 33% smaller than in all previous models. The mass model appears\nto be particularly well constrained in the MDLF region. We characterize the\nrobustness of the magnification map at varying distances from the model\ncritical lines and the total projected mass profile of the cluster.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Sep 2020 18:01:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 19 Nov 2020 18:13:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-27"}
