 step towards a quantum\ncomputing algorithm to describe the full collision event at the LHC.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Sep 2020 18:26:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 13 Oct 2020 17:05:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-05"}
